[section#basic.extended.fp
    [:en] Optional extended floating-point types
    [:zh_CN] 可选的扩充浮点类型
]

[para]
[:en]
If the implementation supports an extended floating-point type
([#basic.fundamental]) whose properties are specified by the ISO/IEC/IEEE 60559
floating-point interchange format binary16, then the [~typedef-name]
[`std::float16_t] is defined in the header [?libheader@ref stdfloat] and names
such a type, the macro [`__STDCPP_FLOAT16_T__] is defined ([#cpp.predefined]),
and the floating-point literal suffixes [`f16] and [`F16] are supported
([#lex.fcon]).
[:zh_CN]
如果实现支持的某个扩充浮点类型（[#basic.fundamental]）具有由 ISO/IEC/IEEE 60559
浮点交换格式 binary16 所规定的属性，则在头文件 [?libheader@ref stdfloat] 中定义
[~typedef-名] [`std::float16_t] 并指名这种类型，定义宏 [`__STDCPP_FLOAT16_T__]
（[#cpp.predefined]），并支持浮点字面量后缀 [`f16] 和 [`F16]（[#lex.fcon]）。

[para]
[:en]
If the implementation supports an extended floating-point type whose properties
are specified by the ISO/IEC/IEEE 60559 floating-point interchange format
binary32, then the [~typedef-name] [`std::float32_t] is defined in the header
[?libheader stdfloat] and names such a type, the macro [`__STDCPP_FLOAT32_T__]
is defined, and the floating-point literal suffixes [`f32] and [`F32] are
