[para:recommended]
[:en]
Any names that the implementation provides for the extended floating-point types
described in this subsection that are in addition to the names defined in the
[?libheader stdfloat] header should be chosen to increase compatibility and
interoperability with the interchange types [`_Float16], [`_Float32], [`_Float64],
and [`_Float128] defined in ISO/IEC TS 18661-3 and with future versions of
[=IsoCUndated].
[:zh_CN]
除了头文件 [?libheader stdfloat] 中定义的名字之外，实现为本子条款所描述的扩充
浮点类型所提供的任何其他名字，它们的选取应当提升与 ISO/IEC TS 18661-3 中定义的
交换类型 [`_Float16]、[`_Float32]、[`_Float64] 和 [`_Float128] 之间，以及与
[=IsoCUndated] 的未来版本之间的兼容性和互操作性。
